reviewText:
Perfect Halloween cartoons!
Frankenpooh, more addicting then pumpkin spice!
We collected all the VHS tapes in back then for our children. They are play good & kids like them very much. Thank you & have a good weekend!
My son loves this tape - he watches it over and over.  These older Winnie the Pooh stories are great. They don't have the intensity of the newer movies - which is just right for young children.
